    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在这款垃圾塔防策略游戏中保卫您的家园免受污染威胁!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 敌对国家正朝您发射充满垃圾的气球，试图用污染淹没你的家园. 面对这场污染威胁，你必须奋起反击，建造强大的炮塔，把垃圾送回敌人的地盘!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>建造与升级炮塔</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏初期，你将亲自操作炮塔，精准瞄准来袭的垃圾并将其击落。随后，你可以升级并自动化防御系统，同时尝试不同的炮塔和升级组合，打造专属策略!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139380/extras/978c429acd3bde1306793386e75d7826.poster.avif?t=1767656636\" width=616 height=217 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139380/extras/978c429acd3bde1306793386e75d7826.webm?t=1767656636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>策略性基地建设</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建设建筑来强化你的防御和攻击，将垃圾与意外惊喜送回敌人身上！别忘了有效管理资金，平衡投入防御与资源增长.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139380/extras/f8d26140223d94bbdafd5332444e538b.poster.avif?t=1767656636\" width=616 height=217 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139380/extras/f8d26140223d94bbdafd5332444e538b.webm?t=1767656636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>敌人千变万化，挑战层出不穷!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索不同类型的敌人，了解他们的特性与弱点，并设法突破对手层层防御。随着时间推移，敌人将变得更强大、更狡猾，挑战你的策略极限!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139380/extras/59134a9cc3af418b21db53436b301d4f.poster.avif?t=1767656636\" width=616 height=217 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139380/extras/59134a9cc3af418b21db53436b301d4f.webm?t=1767656636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>生存策略与排行榜挑战</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >资源有限，村民危在旦夕，污染无处不在！掌握每一分资源，建设农场，带领村民迎接挑战。能在这场生死考验中生还，并登上排行榜的巅峰吗?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139380/extras/05d105a2c3b5afc37e89d6bdbe06eb8b.poster.avif?t=1767656636\" width=616 height=217 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139380/extras/05d105a2c3b5afc37e89d6bdbe06eb8b.webm?t=1767656636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
